00:01:32.396 --> 00:01:35.196 A:middle
users, Sign In with Apple is

00:01:35.196 --> 00:01:36.776 A:middle
easier to use than passwords.

00:01:37.986 --> 00:01:40.356 A:middle
People generally don't love

00:01:40.606 --> 00:01:41.626 A:middle
managing passwords.

00:01:42.516 --> 00:01:44.166 A:middle
And when users don't have a

00:01:44.166 --> 00:01:46.386 A:middle
password, that password can't be

00:01:46.386 --> 00:01:48.286 A:middle
a bad password, and it can't get

00:01:48.286 --> 00:01:50.136 A:middle
phished, which is good for your

00:01:50.136 --> 00:01:52.136 A:middle
users, but it's also good for

00:01:52.136 --> 00:01:52.446 A:middle
you.

00:01:53.786 --> 00:01:56.306 A:middle
And for you specifically, these

00:01:56.306 --> 00:01:58.526 A:middle
accounts are great accounts.

00:01:59.276 --> 00:02:00.776 A:middle
Every single one of the accounts

00:01:59.276 --> 00:02:00.776 A:middle
Every single one of the accounts

00:02:00.776 --> 00:02:01.926 A:middle
