with Apple has strong two-factor

00:02:04.616 --> 00:02:06.466 A:middle
authentication that's already

00:02:06.466 --> 00:02:08.126 A:middle
used to protect their Apple ID.

00:02:09.006 --> 00:02:10.696 A:middle
