00:02:17.796 --> 00:02:19.706 A:middle
this much security is a lot

00:02:19.706 --> 00:02:21.266 A:middle
easier than trying to bolt it on

00:02:21.266 --> 00:02:22.496 A:middle
after the fact to a

00:02:22.496 --> 00:02:23.516 A:middle
password-based account.

