00:02:28.126 --> 00:02:31.596 A:middle
the API about how Apple is

00:02:31.596 --> 00:02:32.836 A:middle
confident about the account

00:02:32.836 --> 00:02:34.416 A:middle
being from a real user, which

00:02:34.416 --> 00:02:34.986 A:middle
you're going to really

00:02:34.986 --> 00:02:36.106 A:middle
appreciate.

