00:02:38.286 --> 00:02:39.696 A:middle
to emphasize about Sign In with

00:02:39.696 --> 00:02:42.636 A:middle
Apple is that it is across

00:02:42.836 --> 00:02:45.976 A:middle
platform experience, across all

00:02:45.976 --> 00:02:47.126 A:middle
of the user's devices.

00:02:47.476 --> 00:02:48.456 A:middle
If they're signed into their

00:02:48.456 --> 00:02:50.966 A:middle
Apple ID, signing into your app

