into a single window.

00:15:16.186 --> 00:15:19.136 A:middle
But now with iPadOS and macOS

00:15:19.136 --> 00:15:20.686 A:middle
support, you're going to have to

00:15:20.686 --> 00:15:22.076 A:middle
help us out a little bit to

00:15:22.076 --> 00:15:23.106 A:middle
figure out where to draw the

00:15:23.106 --> 00:15:23.686 A:middle
interface.

00:15:25.056 --> 00:15:28.726 A:middle
First, you'll give the session a

00:15:28.726 --> 00:15:30.746 A:middle
presentationContextProvider, and

00:15:31.496 --> 00:15:33.466 A:middle
that presentationContextProvider

00:15:33.796 --> 00:15:35.606 A:middle
will provide a window via the

00:15:35.606 --> 00:15:36.896 A:middle
PresentationAnchor method.

00:15:37.786 --> 00:15:39.316 A:middle
This is a really easy change and

00:15:39.316 --> 00:15:40.946 A:middle
one that you're definitely going

00:15:40.946 --> 00:15:43.926 A:middle
to want to make.

00:15:43.926 --> 00:15:45.026 A:middle
One more thing about OAuth.

