It's from the Safari Services

00:15:54.116 --> 00:15:54.526 A:middle
framework.

00:15:55.536 --> 00:15:57.046 A:middle
If you haven't already, you're

00:15:57.046 --> 00:15:58.076 A:middle
going to want to take a moment

00:15:58.076 --> 00:15:58.916 A:middle
to switch over.

00:16:00.066 --> 00:16:02.216 A:middle
ASWebAuthenticationSession has

